Santander, BBVA Are Favorites to Buy CAM Bank, Economista Says

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-04-01T05:24:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-01/santander-bbva-are-favorites-to-buy-cam-bank-economista-says.html
Banco Santander SA (SAN)  is the favorite
candidate to buy  Caja de Ahorros del Mediterraneo (CAM) , the savings
bank the Bank of  Spain  wants to sell,  El Economista  reported,
citing unidentified people in the financial industry.  The regulator may try to auction CAM this weekend , the
newspaper said.  Banco Bilbao Vizcaya Argentaria SA (BBVA)  is the second most
favored buyer for the Alicante-based bank, which may need a
capital injection of as much as 3 billion euros ($3.25 billion),
the newspaper said.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Sharon Smyth in Madrid at   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Blackman at   ablackman@bloomberg.net . 